        "new_string": "/**\n * Priority information for an easy handle in relation to others\n * on the same connection.\n * Supports both HTTP/2 (weight+dependencies) and HTTP/3 (RFC 9218 urgency+incremental)\n */\nstruct Curl_data_priority {\n#ifdef USE_NGHTTP2\n  /* tree like dependencies only implemented in nghttp2 */\n  struct Curl_easy *parent;\n  struct Curl_data_prio_node *children;\n#endif\n  int weight;\n#ifdef USE_NGHTTP2\n  BIT(exclusive);\n#endif\n#if defined(USE_HTTP3)\n  /* HTTP/3 RFC 9218 Extensible Priorities */\n  unsigned int urgency;  /* 0-7, default 3 */\n  BIT(incremental);      /* incremental flag */\n#endif\n};",
